{
  "texts": [
    "A Prompting ChatGPTThe full prompt and the answer of ChatGPT for the example task loops/co-unt_up_down-1 is shown in Figure 5.",
    "We use the same prompt for all tasks.",
    "The answer of ChatGPT can slightly vary between executions.",
    "Therefore, we generate up to k answers and collect invariants from all answers via a regular expression.Prompt> Compute a loop invariant for the annotated loop including [invariant] in the following C code.",
    "Please use the format of ACSL annotations and always end your response with //@ loop invariant X; where X is the computed invariant."
  ]
}